{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(cm)multiPolygonWithPolygons:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"polygons","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The array of polygons defining the shape."}]}],"name":"polygons"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A new multipolygon object.","type":"text"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","role":"symbol","title":"MLNPolygon","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"d